HEADWORD: Phalænid
<hw>Pha*l⟦ae⟧"nid</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>fa`laina</grk>, <grk>fa`llaina</grk>, a kind of moth.]</ety>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Any moth of the family
